        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎬 Movie Trailer Generator\n\nType one logline and the canvas builds a narrated teaser. Prompt nodes do the work: one templates the inputs into a trailer treatment, one turns each generated shot into full cinematic key art, and one writes the voiceover.\n\n**Pipeline:** Logline → Treatment prompt → Shot prompts → Keyframe prompt → Text-to-Image → Cut + AI narration\n\n**Try this:** change the visual style or shot count, swap the image/voice model. For full motion, replace Frames-to-Video with per-shot Image-to-Video + Concat."
        },
